Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.76,0:00:42.63,OPC,,0,0,0,,Spark me up! check check check!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.68,0:00:46.57,OPC,,0,0,0,,未能满足 想被看透
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.64,0:00:50.60,OPC,,0,0,0,,想把这份感情变成蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.70,0:00:54.72,OPC,,0,0,0,,想更深入 已经按耐不住
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.74,0:00:58.35,OPC,,0,0,0,,希望得到上天的启示
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.37,0:01:00.50,OPC,,0,0,0,,无需搅乱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.52,0:01:02.44,OPC,,0,0,0,,一直当个好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.47,0:01:04.54,OPC,,0,0,0,,妄想的日常
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.57,0:01:06.51,OPC,,0,0,0,,不会崩坏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.51,0:01:08.50,OPC,,0,0,0,,虽想要呼喊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.50,0:01:10.47,OPC,,0,0,0,,然而微弱的叹息中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.47,0:01:14.46,OPC,,0,0,0,,咒语并未起效
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.46,0:01:15.80,OPC,,0,0,0,,（Go ready Go）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.80,0:01:18.58,OPC,,0,0,0,,今天来一场赌博吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.64,0:01:22.03,OPC,,0,0,0,,陷入听天由命的未知中 (Go baby NEW-NEW)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.03,0:01:24.48,OPC,,0,0,0,,度过吧 (Go,baby NEW-WAY NEW-WAY)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.48,0:01:26.53,OPC,,0,0,0,,变得狂野吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.53,0:01:29.90,OPC,,0,0,0,,向着恋爱的秘境 (Go baby NEW-NEW)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.90,0:01:32.54,OPC,,0,0,0,,进发 (Go,baby NEW-WAY NEW-WAY)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.54,0:01:34.57,OPC,,0,0,0,,黄昏之时
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.67,0:01:36.99,OPC,,0,0,0,,不管何事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.28,0:01:41.55,OPC,,0,0,0,,都让我们在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.65,0:01:43.56,OPC,,0,0,0,,NOW·NOW·NOW·NOW
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.64,0:01:45.57,OPC,,0,0,0,,NEW·NEW·NEW·NEW
